name: Farewell US Airways | An FSX Movie
description:
Hey everyone, this is my very first Flight Simulator X Movie, and it's a tribute to US Airways, which is merging with American Airlines. Since it's my first FSX Movie, it's not very good, but I'm learning as I go. I hope you enjoy, and please comment, rate, and subscribe!

Music is "Decline" by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
